<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs fehna chia hocha,
 Ʋlla sia hoka
 Is sa̱ nukha̱klo pullashke;
 Chim asilhha lishke.

[V2]
 Chim aiahni bieka hosh,
 A̱ nukha̱klokmʋto,
 Sa chu̱kʋsh anu̱kaka ya̱
 Foho̱ka pullashke.

[V3]
 Ʋlla sʋlbʋsha't sʋlla chi̱;
 Chisʋs pulla hokʋt
 Ʋlla ʋno chohmi hoka,
 I̱ hullo hak inli.

[V4]
 Aiahni bieka hocha,
 Isht chi taloho̱ʋt
 Shutik tʋboka pilla ka
 Pit e pihinlashke.

[V5]
 Ʋlla pi fehna hoh kia,
 E chi aiokpanchi;
 Ilʋppa fehna pulla ka
 Ish pi nukha̱klashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs fehna chia hocha</aka>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>For Children. A Prayer. ƲIT124</title>
<author>David Folsom</author>
<hymn_number>124</hymn_number>
</song>